<collectingRegion box="[925,1041,1731,1764]" country="Indonesia" name="Sulawesi Utara" pageId="53" pageNumber="111">Sulawesi</collectingRegion>
(including Togian and Muna Is) and Sula Is (Mangole, Sanana); it probably occurs on all of Togian Isand possibly occurs on Buton I.
</paragraph>
